181/*******************************************************************************
182 * PGRAPH engine/subdev functions
183 ******************************************************************************/
184
185int
186gk104_gr_init(struct gf100_gr *gr)
187{
188 struct nvkm_device *device = gr->base.engine.subdev.device;
189 const u32 magicgpc918 = DIV_ROUND_UP(0x00800000, gr->tpc_total);
190 u32 data[TPC_MAX / 8] = {};
191 u8 tpcnr[GPC_MAX];
192 int gpc, tpc, rop;
193 int i;
194
195 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0880), 0x00000000);
196 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x08a4), 0x00000000);
197 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0888), 0x00000000);
198 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x088c), 0x00000000);
199 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0890), 0x00000000);
200 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0894), 0x00000000);
201 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x08b4), nvkm_memory_addr(gr->unk4188b4) >> 8);
202 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x08b8), nvkm_memory_addr(gr->unk4188b8) >> 8);
203
204 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, gr->func->mmio);
205
206 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(0, 0x3018), 0x00000001);
207
208 memset(data, 0x00, sizeof(data));
209 memcpy(tpcnr, gr->tpc_nr, sizeof(gr->tpc_nr));
210 for (i = 0, gpc = -1; i < gr->tpc_total; i++) {
211 do {
212 gpc = (gpc + 1) % gr->gpc_nr;
213 } while (!tpcnr[gpc]);
214 tpc = gr->tpc_nr[gpc] - tpcnr[gpc]--;
215
216 data[i / 8] |= tpc << ((i % 8) * 4);
217 }
218
219 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0980), data[0]);
220 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0984), data[1]);
221 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0988), data[2]);
222 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x098c), data[3]);
223
224 for (gpc = 0; gpc < gr->gpc_nr; gpc++) {
225 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0914),
226 gr->magic_not_rop_nr << 8 | gr->tpc_nr[gpc]);
227 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0910), 0x00040000 |
228 gr->tpc_total);
229 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0918), magicgpc918);
230 }
231
232 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x3fd4), magicgpc918);
233 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x08ac), nvkm_rd32(device, 0x100800));
234
235 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400500, 0x00010001);
236
237 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400100, 0xffffffff);
238 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x40013c, 0xffffffff);
239
240 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x409ffc, 0x00000000);
241 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x409c14, 0x00003e3e);
242 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x409c24, 0x000f0001);
243 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404000, 0xc0000000);
244 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404600, 0xc0000000);
245 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x408030, 0xc0000000);
246 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404490, 0xc0000000);
247 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x406018, 0xc0000000);
248 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x407020, 0x40000000);
249 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x405840, 0xc0000000);
250 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x405844, 0x00ffffff);
251 nvkm_mask(device, 0x419cc0, 0x00000008, 0x00000008);
252 nvkm_mask(device, 0x419eb4, 0x00001000, 0x00001000);
253
254 for (gpc = 0; gpc < gr->gpc_nr; gpc++) {
255 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x3038), 0xc0000000);
256 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0420), 0xc0000000);
257 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0900), 0xc0000000);
258 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x1028), 0xc0000000);
259 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0824), 0xc0000000);
260 for (tpc = 0; tpc < gr->tpc_nr[gpc]; tpc++) {
261 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x508), 0xffffffff);
262 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x50c), 0xffffffff);
263 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x224), 0xc0000000);
264 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x48c), 0xc0000000);
265 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x084), 0xc0000000);
266 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x644), 0x001ffffe);
267 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x64c), 0x0000000f);
268 }
269 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x2c90), 0xffffffff);
270 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x2c94), 0xffffffff);
271 }
272
273 for (rop = 0; rop < gr->rop_nr; rop++) {
274 nvkm_wr32(device, ROP_UNIT(rop, 0x144), 0xc0000000);
275 nvkm_wr32(device, ROP_UNIT(rop, 0x070), 0xc0000000);
276 nvkm_wr32(device, ROP_UNIT(rop, 0x204), 0xffffffff);
277 nvkm_wr32(device, ROP_UNIT(rop, 0x208), 0xffffffff);
278 }
279
280 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400108, 0xffffffff);
281 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400138, 0xffffffff);
282 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400118, 0xffffffff);
283 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400130, 0xffffffff);
284 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x40011c, 0xffffffff);
285 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400134, 0xffffffff);
286
287 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400054, 0x34ce3464);
288
289 gf100_gr_zbc_init(gr);
290
291 return gf100_gr_init_ctxctl(gr);
292}

315gk104_gr = {

317 .mmio = gk104_gr_pack_mmio,
318 .fecs.ucode = &gk104_gr_fecs_ucode,

334 return gf100_gr_new_(&gk104_gr, device, index, pgr);
